{"tid":1924832,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國exchange]大家留定走","createTime":"2020-03-14T02:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T18:21:27.000Z","uid":275243,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f4043c40b301551a4c73c4da0b22d4e519dcec88","tid":1924832,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:37:47.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學校今日宣布停課<br />\n之後轉做online learning<br />\n鼓勵學生返自己屋企<br />\n同埋唔知香港正苦會唔會失驚無神整個紅色外遊警示<br />\nUST規定一出就要返<br />\n(本身以為香港正苦唔會敢對美國出<br />\n但係今朝佢一出就對成個神根出真心嚇一跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n所以我都諗住買機票返香港<br />\n但係好擔心係機場/機上中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有口罩諗緊使唔使眼罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋應該揀直航定轉機好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飛機上係咪唔應該食飯<br />\n一係就食完換新口罩<br />\n有無係美國exchange嘅同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2042b2494ec6313c8dc7e7c67a735026a5c4d07e","tid":1924832,"uid":30836,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"如果冇咩咪留喺美國<br />\n安全啲喎搭少程飛機..."},{"pid":"af0f789effded56c1c97d78a9f6d12295020f8da","tid":1924832,"uid":275243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2042b2494ec6313c8dc7e7c67a735